# Uniswap v4

Custom hook development for on-chain swap logic.
- SDKs: `@uniswap/v4-sdk`, `@uniswap/sdk-core`
- Solidity: use Foundry (`forge build`, `forge test`)
- v4 core: https://github.com/Uniswap/v4-core
- v4 periphery: https://github.com/Uniswap/v4-periphery
- Hooks run custom logic before/after swaps, liquidity changes, etc.
